---
tags:[shutdown]
---
# To reboot the system immediately:
# 立即重启
shutdown -r now

# To shut system down immediately:
# 立即关机
shutdown -h now

# To reboot system after 5 minutes:
# 5分钟后重启
shutdown -r +5

# 5:30 关机
shutdown -h 05:30

# To cancel a scheduled shutdown:
# 取消已经执行的 shutdown 命令
shutdown -c
